  "detailed_description": "Welcome to Egression, Inc., home of the world’s most deluxe escape room experiences. Grab your favorite VR headset, and get locked inside innovative spaces designed specifically for puzzlers like you. Explore your surroundings. Solve puzzles. Find the key to your escape.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384940/extras/3997a6feadb5dc365b744d852ecef95d.poster.avif?t=1745976353\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384940/extras/3997a6feadb5dc365b744d852ecef95d.webm?t=1745976353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384940/extras/3997a6feadb5dc365b744d852ecef95d.mp4?t=1745976353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Explore engaging environments:</strong> Walk freely through the escape room establishment, complete your escape artist training, and traverse through two unique escape rooms devised from the ground up just for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384940/extras/053a5b57d990818f8fea7c2b2549f843.poster.avif?t=1745976353\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384940/extras/053a5b57d990818f8fea7c2b2549f843.webm?t=1745976353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384940/extras/053a5b57d990818f8fea7c2b2549f843.mp4?t=1745976353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Inspect intriguing objects:</strong> Analyze everything around you. Leave no stone unturned. Piece together the clues until the path forward becomes clear.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384940/extras/e03911e12157cea3100b8988b06b1806.poster.avif?t=1745976353\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384940/extras/e03911e12157cea3100b8988b06b1806.webm?t=1745976353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384940/extras/e03911e12157cea3100b8988b06b1806.mp4?t=1745976353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Solve puzzles:</strong> Challenge your mind with realistic escape room style puzzles made for VR. Solve your way from one \"Aha!\" moment to the next.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384940/extras/512ee1d0c0d8973cad51dad89faaff40.poster.avif?t=1745976353\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384940/extras/512ee1d0c0d8973cad51dad89faaff40.webm?t=1745976353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384940/extras/512ee1d0c0d8973cad51dad89faaff40.mp4?t=1745976353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Escape:</strong> Accomplish what you set out to do: escape rooms. Puzzle your way through the Game Room. And then, if you’re itching for more, challenge yourself to the Deep Sea Lab.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384940/extras/6422ea24842f4de16cd64e7ead4c35d6.poster.avif?t=1745976353\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384940/extras/6422ea24842f4de16cd64e7ead4c35d6.webm?t=1745976353\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1384940/extras/6422ea24842f4de16cd64e7ead4c35d6.mp4?t=1745976353\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Break stuff:</strong> And of course, every VR gamer’s dream - throw things on the floor to see if they break. (Some do!)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore <strong>immersive</strong> environments<br></li><li><strong>Interact</strong> with all objects you can see<br></li><li>Solve <strong>unique handcrafted puzzles</strong><br></li><li><strong>Escape</strong> two rooms<br></li><li>Play through <strong>4-6 hours</strong> of content (depending on the level of your puzzle-solving skills)</li></ul><br>If you're a fan of escape room style puzzle games like The Room VR: A Dark Matter, I Expect You To Die, Wanderer, and Escape Simulator, you're going to have an amazing time within the halls of Egression, Inc.!",
